      "start_time": 501094.0,
      "end_time": 505632.0,
      "text": "Part of the magic here is the facial expressions."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 505632.0,
      "end_time": 509785.0,
      "text": "Previously, robot and animatronics has  a kind of stiff faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 509785.0,
      "end_time": 512701.0,
      "text": "It was hard to get them to move into  realistic face expressions."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 512701.0,
      "end_time": 518544.0,
      "text": "So part of my phd research was tackling  this material science problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 518544.0,
      "end_time": 523648.0,
      "text": "So I analyzed the physics of human  facial expression a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 523648.0,
      "end_time": 529890.0,
      "text": "The liquid is critical for human facial expressions."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 529890.0,
      "end_time": 532893.0,
      "text": "A low power facial expressions that our faces achieve."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 532893.0,
      "end_time": 538880.0,
      "text": "So I developed with a friend of mine at  Jet Propulsion Laboratory, Victor White"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 538880.0,
      "end_time": 541509.0,
      "text": "a new material that is"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 541509.0,
      "end_time": 546839.0,
      "text": "based on the same physics as human  facial expression materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 546839.0,
      "end_time": 550656.0,
      "text": "and there is alipid bilayer"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 550656.0,
      "end_time": 553112.0,
      "text": "a fat, but basically what that means is"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 553112.0,
      "end_time": 555814.0,
      "text": "you get the cells of self-assemble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 555814.0,
      "end_time": 558183.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re filled with the fluid."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 558183.0,
      "end_time": 560406.0,
      "text": "And then it just takes very little force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 560406.0,
      "end_time": 562521.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s extremely elastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 562521.0,
      "end_time": 564223.0,
      "text": "And their expressions, facial expressions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 564223.0,
      "end_time": 566322.0,
      "text": "just naturally fall into place."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 566322.0,
      "end_time": 571531.0,
      "text": "Now you also need some mechanics to get the  facial expressions to move correctly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 571531.0,
      "end_time": 575155.0,
      "text": "with anchors that are embedded in the material  in the right way."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 575155.0,
      "end_time": 576969.0,
      "text": "But when you do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 576969.0,
      "end_time": 579206.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s very very simple"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 579206.0,
      "end_time": 581277.0,
      "text": "to achieve facial expressions like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 581277.0,
      "end_time": 583110.0,
      "text": "You can do it with very few motors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 583110.0,
      "end_time": 590268.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s what we are doing in products now  that we&#39;re manufacturing"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 590268.0,
      "end_time": 596535.0,
      "text": "So this just shows you a basic range of  facial expressions of one of our robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 596535.0,
      "end_time": 598424.0,
      "text": "This robot is called Diego-San."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 598424.0,
      "end_time": 600334.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the collaboration of the University of California"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 600334.0,
      "end_time": 603505.0,
      "text": "and San Diego Machine Perception Laboratory."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 603505.0,
      "end_time": 606975.0,
      "text": "The body is built by the Kokoro Company of Tokyo."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 606975.0,
      "end_time": 608698.0,
      "text": "The head was built by me and my company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 608698.0,
      "end_time": 610529.0,
      "text": "Hanson Robotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 610529.0,
      "end_time": 617183.0,
      "text": "and this project was founded by the National Science Foundation of the Unite States."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 617183.0,
      "end_time": 619350.0,
      "text": "So we can pretty much achieve"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 619350.0,
      "end_time": 621289.0,
      "text": "any facial expressions you named it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 621289.0,
      "end_time": 622957.0,
      "text": "no matter how subtle, we can get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 622957.0,
      "end_time": 625257.0,
      "text": "Now taking those, kinds of face, faces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 625257.0,
      "end_time": 627637.0,
      "text": "facial expressions and physical bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 627637.0,
      "end_time": 629695.0,
      "text": "and empowering it with the A.I.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 629695.0,
      "end_time": 634000.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s where you get this amazing way of  interfacing with the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 634000.0,
      "end_time": 636603.0,
      "text": "You can get all kinds of unstructured data from the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 636603.0,
      "end_time": 638202.0,
      "text": "from interactions with people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 638202.0,
      "end_time": 640706.0,
      "text": "and use that to sort of scaffold these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 640706.0,
      "end_time": 643041.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re literally like babies right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 643041.0,
      "end_time": 646409.0,
      "text": "so we need to nurture them among us."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 646409.0,
      "end_time": 650615.0,
      "text": "Previously, artificial intelligence initiative  are often fractured."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 650615.0,
      "end_time": 653485.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got machine perceptions people working over here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 653485.0,
      "end_time": 657154.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got the statistic learning people over here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 657154.0,
      "end_time": 660462.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got the robotics control people in these groups..."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 660462.0,
      "end_time": 662220.0,
      "text": "And these sort of, sometimes communicate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 662220.0,
      "end_time": 664687.0,
      "text": "but they don&#39;t coordinate on something"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 664687.0,
      "end_time": 670394.0,
      "text": "that is like a major worldwide concerted effort"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 670394.0,
      "end_time": 672596.0,
      "text": "to achieve human level cognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 672596.0,
      "end_time": 675373.0,
      "text": "So some friends of mine and I are working"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 675373.0,
      "end_time": 678375.0,
      "text": "to bridge these various fields as best as we can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 678375.0,
      "end_time": 683782.0,
      "text": "to integrate into a more cohesive complex  intelligence systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 683782.0,
      "end_time": 686545.0,
      "text": "So we made all of our source code open source."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 686545.0,
      "end_time": 689419.0,
      "text": "We divided into two blocks of categories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 689419.0,
      "end_time": 691688.0,
      "text": "one is that pieces that glue things together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 691688.0,
      "end_time": 693292.0,
      "text": "the glued A.I.;"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 693292.0,
      "end_time": 697729.0,
      "text": "and the other the kind that is actually intelligent  and it interacts with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 697729.0,
      "end_time": 703347.0,
      "text": "and we call it generational A.I., Genie."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 703347.0,
      "end_time": 707982.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve achieved a lot of natural interactions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 707982.0,
      "end_time": 711409.0,
      "text": "including facial expression mimicry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 711409.0,
      "end_time": 715346.0,
      "text": "facial expression recognition processing the meaning of these facial expressions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 715346.0,
      "end_time": 716813.0,
      "text": "natural language dialog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 716813.0,
      "end_time": 723630.0,
      "text": "movie quality tools animating the robots  for a more natural interaction."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 723630.0,
      "end_time": 731262.0,
      "text": "We also have a fairly sophisticated theory of mind system"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 731262.0,
      "end_time": 733129.0,
      "text": "compare to human, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 733129.0,
      "end_time": 738703.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t have a million of years of evolution of  social cognition that we have;"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 738703.0,
      "end_time": 743538.0,
      "text": "however, this theory of mind can predict  what you&#39;re thinking and feeling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 743538.0,
      "end_time": 745776.0,
      "text": "and makes some decision about"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 745776.0,
      "end_time": 748144.0,
      "text": "what its goal are vs. what your goals are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 748144.0,
      "end_time": 752183.0,
      "text": "in order to understand you and empathize with you better."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 752183.0,
      "end_time": 755219.0,
      "text": "We have a prototype form of consciousness."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 755219.0,
      "end_time": 757421.0,
      "text": "We had the robot can self-reflect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 757421.0,
      "end_time": 759288.0,
      "text": "reflect on what it&#39;s thinking and feeling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 759288.0,
      "end_time": 763059.0,
      "text": "and try to imagine results for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 763059.0,
      "end_time": 768368.0,
      "text": "So we also have a collaboration on a bridges with the OpenCog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 768368.0,
      "end_time": 773269.0,
      "text": "which is a very large artificial general intelligence project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 773269.0,
      "end_time": 776455.0,
      "text": "robot operating systems and android operating system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 776455.0,
      "end_time": 778174.0,
      "text": "and numerals other projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 778174.0,
      "end_time": 780111.0,
      "text": "bringing these fields together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 780111.0,
      "end_time": 781912.0,
      "text": "then allow us to do more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 781912.0,
      "end_time": 783481.0,
      "text": "and allows you to do more."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 783481.0,
      "end_time": 785955.0,
      "text": "Anybody in the world can build their own product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 785955.0,
      "end_time": 788221.0,
      "text": "do new research, do psychology research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 788221.0,
      "end_time": 792348.0,
      "text": "to study how humans and robots are interacting."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 792348.0,
      "end_time": 796760.0,
      "text": "So we are seeking more than mere  intelligence in the machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 796760.0,
      "end_time": 798863.0,
      "text": "Sure, intelligent machines are useful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 798863.0,
      "end_time": 800172.0,
      "text": "and increasingly useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 800172.0,
      "end_time": 803005.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re increasingly commoner in our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 803005.0,
      "end_time": 806870.0,
      "text": "Things that scientists, respected scientists said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 806870.0,
      "end_time": 809499.0,
      "text": "we just should not expect in our life time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 809499.0,
      "end_time": 811291.0,
      "text": "five years later, happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 811291.0,
      "end_time": 812375.0,
      "text": "They just happened, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 812375.0,
      "end_time": 817847.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re building, we&#39;re making strides  in these directions."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 817847.0,
      "end_time": 822753.0,
      "text": "If we can achieve greater levels of intelligence  in these machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 822753.0,
      "end_time": 825220.0,
      "text": "we can achieve genius machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 825220.0,
      "end_time": 828959.0,
      "text": "They can help us solve some of the  world&#39;s hard problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 828959.0,
      "end_time": 831181.0,
      "text": "In some regards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 831181.0,
      "end_time": 834633.0,
      "text": "A.I. is now so brilliant"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 834633.0,
      "end_time": 838536.0,
      "text": "that it can see things in data that we can&#39;t see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 838536.0,
      "end_time": 841173.0,
      "text": "the big data that&#39;s called,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 841173.0,
      "end_time": 844514.0,
      "text": "is approach that is yielding tremendous results."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 844514.0,
      "end_time": 847943.0,
      "text": "We already have genius machines in some regards."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 847943.0,
      "end_time": 851750.0,
      "text": "Imagine the machines can look at bigger problems like"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 851750.0,
      "end_time": 855385.0,
      "text": "you know, clean water, and clean energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 855385.0,
      "end_time": 858689.0,
      "text": "sustainable agriculture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 858689.0,
      "end_time": 862635.0,
      "text": "and come up with creative solutions with their imaginations."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 862635.0,
      "end_time": 865634.0,
      "text": "That would make it difference in the history of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 865634.0,
      "end_time": 868232.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re creating problems very quickly actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 868232.0,
      "end_time": 869767.0,
      "text": "Some of the solutions we come up with"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 869767.0,
      "end_time": 871802.0,
      "text": "have unintended consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 871802.0,
      "end_time": 874272.0,
      "text": "We need to get smarter as civilization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 874272.0,
      "end_time": 877774.0,
      "text": "and A.I. is one way that we can do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 877774.0,
      "end_time": 881245.0,
      "text": "The question is here, of course, what is Genius?"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 881245.0,
      "end_time": 883884.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 883884.0,
      "end_time": 885149.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s more than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 885149.0,
      "end_time": 887651.0,
      "text": "If you historically look at all examples of human genius,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 887651.0,
      "end_time": 888920.0,
      "text": "it is beyond that."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 888920.0,
      "end_time": 890987.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 890987.0,
      "end_time": 893190.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re looking in the emergence and creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 893190.0,
      "end_time": 896293.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hot topic of research."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 896293.0,
      "end_time": 897968.0,
      "text": "So, it&#39;s not just,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 897968.0,
      "end_time": 900857.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s psychology neuroscience complexity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 900857.0,
      "end_time": 904070.0,
      "text": "and also the arts."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 904070.0,
      "end_time": 909442.0,
      "text": "So we have good examples of human creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 909442.0,
      "end_time": 913110.0,
      "text": "and the works of Leonardo da Vinci."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 913110.0,
      "end_time": 915486.0,
      "text": "So if you look at some of the capability of"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 915486.0,
      "end_time": 919683.0,
      "text": "these machine that include defense robots and jeopardy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 919683.0,
      "end_time": 922734.0,
      "text": "and the facts are really startling."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 922734.0,
      "end_time": 926657.0,
      "text": "The key here is not just intelligence and creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 926657.0,
      "end_time": 929025.0,
      "text": "but also compassion and wisdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 929025.0,
      "end_time": 931462.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re working to give them the imagination"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 931462.0,
      "end_time": 935499.0,
      "text": "to consider consequences of their actions;"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 935499.0,
      "end_time": 936902.0,
      "text": "how it&#39;s going to affect us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 936902.0,
      "end_time": 940004.0,
      "text": "how to find common good with us and the machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 940004.0,
      "end_time": 943986.0,
      "text": "This is one of the things that our initiative  for Awakening Machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 943986.0,
      "end_time": 946644.0,
      "text": "or, &quot;IAM&quot;, is all about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 946644.0,
      "end_time": 949484.0,
      "text": "to try to achieve not just artificial intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 949484.0,
      "end_time": 951115.0,
      "text": "but also wisdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 951115.0,
      "end_time": 952982.0,
      "text": "And so this collaboration across disciplines"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 952982.0,
      "end_time": 954902.0,
      "text": "becomes incredibly important."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 954902.0,
      "end_time": 958588.0,
      "text": "and open source initiative is their appropriate approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 958588.0,
      "end_time": 961825.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;re also developing a platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 961825.0,
      "end_time": 964028.0,
      "text": "that we called RoboKind."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 964028.0,
      "end_time": 967163.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve put this robot into experiments with kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 967163.0,
      "end_time": 969165.0,
      "text": "artistic kids in particular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 969165.0,
      "end_time": 975566.0,
      "text": "and we have phenomenal, favorable results."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 975566.0,
      "end_time": 980456.0,
      "text": "And we think that together we can build a better future."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 980456.0,
      "end_time": 986017.0,
      "text": "And this kind of surreal reality changing artificial intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 986017.0,
      "end_time": 990154.0,
      "text": "might be good for that kind of future."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 990154.0,
      "end_time": 992039.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like to thank you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 992039.0,
      "end_time": 994058.0,
      "text": "and all of my robots here."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 994058.0,
      "end_time": 995726.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d also like to thank you..."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 995726.0,
      "end_time": 1005726.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}